              <p>Ship high‑quality pages at scale with brand guardrails, approval workflows, and client collaboration tools that streamline your agency process.</p>
              <a href="/solutions/agencies" class="use-case-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Benefits -->
      <section class="section container">
        <h2 class="fade-in">Why teams choose BLDRpage</h2>
        <p class="lead fade-in-delay-1">Built for speed, consistency, and results — everything you need to create better pages faster.</p>
        
        <div class="grid-2 fade-in-delay-2">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Speed Without Sacrifice</h3>
            <p>Go from idea to live page in minutes, not weeks. AI generates complete, professional pages while maintaining your brand standards and conversion best practices.</p>
          </div>
          
